title: Dark Horse Presents 1-25 (Cvrs+Misc Only|2011->|Dgtl|Empire)
description:
This is what's left of Empire's releases of the first twenty-five issues of the current incarnation of the "Dark Horse Presents" anthology, if one trims away all the serialized contents and promotional materials and assorted padding.

In other words, these are the covers, the table of contents pages, and a handful of (mostly top-notch, IMHO) standalone stories and other miscellaneous items which likely won't ever be re-published in another form - unlike many of the serials.

The point? Speaking for myself, I hold on to the ToCs for archival purposes and to the other bits for their own sake, without having several GBs of extraneous content lying around that's already been re-released in more convenient formats. :)
